<p class="">Can the right hon. Gentleman say whether this ship was accompanied by its full complement of protecting destroyers, and whether the Board of Admiralty have had under consideration increasing the protection given to aircraft carriers, which are particularly vulnerable?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
